      • setMapState

        public void setMapState(Map.MapState newMapState)
        Sets the state of the map. Available states are: STATIONARY - Will zoom so the whole route is visible and with pauses and milestones added. NAVIGATION - Zoom to the ground and starts a automatic update of the route to follow the users current location.
        Parameters:
        newMapState, - the new state of the map
